When Jerry commits genocide on an alien planet, only the intergalactic bounty hunter known as JAGUAR can deliver justice. Can Jerry survive Jaguar and his army of goons? Will Rick put family before his loathing of Jerry? Guns, muscles, and flatulence abound in this must-read issue of Rick and Morty Presents!
